Package org.mxupdate.test.data.userinterface

Class Summary
AbstractCommandData<T extends AbstractCommandData<?>> Handles test data for commands / menus.
AbstractUIWithHiddenFlagData<T extends AbstractUIWithHiddenFlagData<?>> Handles user interface test data with hidden flags.
AbstractUIWithSettingData<T extends AbstractUIWithSettingData<?>> Handles user interface test data with settings.
ChannelData Used to define a channel, create them and test the result.
CommandData Used to define a command, create them and test the result.
FieldData<FORMTABLE extends AbstractAdminData<?>> Defines on column / field of a table.
FormData Used to define a web form, create them and test the result.
InquiryData Used to define an inquiry, create them and test the result.
InquiryData.InquiryExportParser The class overwrites the original export parser to handle the embedded inquiry code within configuration item update files.
MenuData Used to define a menu, create them and test the result.
PortalData Used to define a portal, create them and test the result.
TableData Used to define a web table, create them and test the result.
